solution:
Rotating $360^\circ$ is the same as doing nothing, so rotating $510^\circ$ is the same as rotating $510^\circ - 360^\circ = 150^\circ$.  Therefore, we have $\sin 510^\circ = \sin (510^\circ - 360^\circ) = \sin 150^\circ$.

